O Switch se trata de um console híbrido semelhante a um tablet, o qual pode ser acoplado a um dock e, assim, ser transformado em um console de mesa. O console também conta com dois controles sem fio acopláveis de cada lado, chamados pela Nintendo de Joy-Con, que podem ser usados individualmente ou ser acoplados à unidade principal (no modo portátil) ou a uma base semelhante a um gamepad (no modo caseiro). caption.text:
Koholint Island Diorama - Link's Awakening

Just wanted to give a little more of an in depth view of the diorama I made as my entry for the @nintendouk Link's awakening fan art competition.

Inspired by a 2d piece by @willowstration, who recently told me that he had been following my costume work for years, which I was completely flattered by as thier work is stunning. They didn't realise it was me when I asked if I could use his concept and realise it in 3d until I posted it on my Facebook page. 
I'm hoping to make a couple more of these I'm quite happy with the result, mine is happily sitting on a shelf with the rest of my Zelda merch.

I'm still waiting to play links awakening on switch. Patiently waiting for payday to roll in. But I'm making do listening to the amazing soundtrack on YouTube. Tal tal heights is definitely one of my favourite zelda tracks ever and the remake version doesn't disappoint. I can't wait to get my hands on the game.

Издательство Daedalic Entertainment и разработчики из студии Kong Orange определились с датой выхода трёхмерной головоломки Felix the Reaper. На PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One и Nintendo Switch она появится 17 октября.
Главный герой Феликс — сотрудник Министерства Смерти, а его возлюбленная Бетти работает в Министерстве Жизни. Протагонист решает появиться в мире людей в образе Мрачного жнеца, чтобы встретиться с Бетти, и исполняет там свои обязанности — если говорить более точно, то обрекает людей на смерть.
Умирать они будут только в том случае, если Феликсу удастся решить головоломки, двигаясь исключительно в тени. Как и все жнецы, он способен управлять солнцем и менять угол падения тени — судя по всему, на этом и будут построены многие загадки.

Finally trying out copic markers and am enjoying them so far. There are so many things I’m doing that I wish I would have started a long time ago. It took over 10 years for me to really get back into my art and it wasn’t where it should have been when I stopped doing it regularly. I’ve always loved doodling here and there (especially when I was bored) but picking up a pen really opened up some enjoyment that I didn’t know that I will had. I still see myself in an artistic infancy but I can see where I will be in the future and it’s exciting. It’s never too late to start!!!

caption.text:
•Dragon Quest XI 
Streiter des Schicksals 
Definitive Edition S 
Erscheint morgen nun endlich für die Switch! 
Ich muss sagen das diese Demo des Spiels meine erste wirkliche Erfahrung mit Dragon Quest war und mich tatsächlich das Spiel so dermaßen gepackt hat. Ich bin auch einfach ein Riesenfan von dem unverwechselbaren Charakterdesign von Akira Toriyama. Sei es bei Dragon Ball, Dr Slump oder Blue Dragon! Gefällt mir einfach ! An dieser Stelle auch Respekt an Square Enix, die einfach mal eine Demo mit den ersten 10 Stunden Spielzeit des Spiels zur Verfügung stellen, da sollten sich andere Entwickler mal eine Scheibe von abschneiden. Andere fertige spiele enden früher als diese Demo! 
Wie steht ihr zu Dragon Quest ? Seid ihr Fan der Reihe ? Und habt ihr vor es euch für die Switch zu holen ? Lasst es mich wissen ! 🤓

caption.text:
Untitled Goose Game...DEFEATED!!! The first line in the game's description perfectly sums it up; “It’s a lovely morning in the village, and you are a horrible goose.” When I first saw the trailer back at E3, I thought, “No way this is real!” But lo and behold it was, and to be honest...it is probably one of the greatest games I have ever played! Simply put, the game revolves around you, a goose, ruining peoples day by going through a “To-Do List” of hilariously dickish tasks. Steal a child's glasses then trip him in a puddle? CHECK! Trick someone into destroying their neighbours favourite vase? CHECK! Make a gardener hit his finger with a hammer and while he’s on the ground writhing in pain take his hat and run away? DOUBLE CHECK!! The simple, colourful graphics add to the quaint chaos that you unleash upon the world, as does the whimsical piano accompaniment that acts as background music and tension builder. The controls may seem wonky at first, but as you play you really get the feeling that this is how a goose moves! Almost everything you can reach can be interacted with, which allows you to solve the ‘puzzles’ in many different ways. It’s a great introduction for people interested in getting into stealth-based games...or even bird-themed ones if that’s your thing! While the main game is a bit short, there is a time trial mode; but doesn’t really sit well with the relaxing pace the game establishes. I love the title, don’t get me wrong, but a part of me wishes they made an actual title; something like “Goose on the Loose”, “Goose about Town” or “Duck, Duck, JERK!” It’s been a long time since I’ve been this satisfied with a gaming experience, so get this NOW!!! We give this a very solid 5 out of 5 Chug-a-Lugs!

caption.text:
⚔️ I came into Fire Emblem: Three Houses for the tactical gameplay but left with a memorable cast of characters that I won’t soon forget.

The heart of Three Houses lies in its huge cast of likeable characters. I spent countless hours just conversing with my Black Eagle students.

Some of these conversations were hilarious while others were downright depressing. That’s what i loved the most about Three Houses, it made me care. Every character is not what he or she seems at the outset. Your initial reaction to Felix might be that he’s an asshole. Fair enough. But once you get to know the “why”, you can’t help but feel heartbroken for him.

Even after 101 hours, I barely scratched the surface. The game encourages multiple playthroughs to know the whole story. Yes, it’s a huge time investment but with a cast of characters this strong it’s worth seeing how everything plays out.

Who was your favorite Three Houses character? Let me know!

Check out awesome accounts tagged!

Gaming Partners
@herooftime88
@ca_gaming1415
@highscorejeffy
.
.
🇩🇴 ⚔️ El corazón de Three Houses reside en su enorme elenco de personajes agradables. Pasé incontables horas conversando con mis estudiantes de Black Eagle.

Algunas de estas conversaciones fueron divertidas, mientras que otras fueron francamente deprimentes. Eso fue lo que más me gustó de Three Houses. Todos los personajes no son lo que parecen cuando lo conoces. Tu reacción inicial a Felix podría ser que es un imbécil. Pero una vez que conoces el "por qué" el es así, no puedes evitar sentirte triste por él.

Después de 101 horas, solo he visto una pizca de la historia completa. El juego fomenta múltiples juegos para conocer toda la historia. Sí, es una gran inversión de tiempo, pero con un elenco de personajes tan fuertes, vale la pena ver cómo se termina todo. ¿Quién fue tu personaje favorito de Three Houses? ¡Házmelo saber!
